<br>
Note about enraging weapons, they should be bagged until its your turn to tank...at that point you use AE taunt and unbag your ragers.  Thus there is no need to constantly use those weapons unless you are actively being the main. In that case you don't care about your dps, just staying alive.<br>
 <p>Dracon Battlehammer<br>
Magister<br>
